nodeOptions_

private boolean[] nodeOptions_
Boolean array for storing node display options. The option sequence is; visibility, labels, restraints, springs, mechanical loads, displacement loads, masses, local axes, initial displacements, initial velocities, groups.

nodeVizOptions_

private double[] nodeVizOptions_
Double array for storing the visualization option of nodes. The first three values are the rgb values of the color (which is light gray as default), the last value is the opacity (which is no-transparent by default).

elementOptions_

private boolean[] elementOptions_
Boolean array for storing element display options. The option sequence is; visibility, labels, extrude, mechanical loads, temperature loads, masses, materials, sections, springs, local axes, element types, groups, upside down, inside out, zero volume, aspect ratio.

elementVizOptions_

private double[] elementVizOptions_
Double array for storing the visualization option of elements. The first three values are the rgb values of the color (which is light gray as default), the last value is the opacity (which is no-transparent by default).

maxDistance_

private double maxDistance_
Maximum and minimum distances between nodes. Used for scaling objects.

minDistance_

private double minDistance_
Maximum and minimum distances between nodes. Used for scaling objects.

treshold_

private double treshold_
Treshold value for displaying bad aspect ratio elements.

factors_

private double[] factors_
Array storing the scaling factors of drawing. The sequence is; radius of nodes, radius of lines, radius of arrows, length of arrows, text height, writing tolerance.
